summary_text: 1. I lived in a small apartment near the city center. 2. I started my first job as a graphic designer. 3. My father was recovering from surgery and used a wheelchair. 4. A kind neighbor was the only person with my father during the day. 5. I had a strong feeling to pray for my father's recovery at a park. 6. I went to the park during my lunch break to pray. 7. I whispered a prayer under a big oak tree for my father. 8. I received a text from my father saying he took steps with his walker. 9. I rushed home and saw my father standing with his walker. 10. My father now walks without assistance and enjoys life in his seventies.
